The '''''Bilbringi''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] used by the [[Habassa]]. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|frigate]] ''[[Mayhem]]'' attempted to attack the ''[[Filve]]'' and the ''Bilbringi'' believing it to be a secret meeting between the Rebels and the Habassa. However, the Rebels leaked the information intending to capture the ''Mayhem''. The operation was a success.

